title: Mandarin Orange Vegetable Stir-Fry
instructions: In a large skillet, heat the oil over medium heat. Stir-fry the vegetables until crisp-tender. Add in the spaghetti noodles & allow the noodles to heat through, stirring frequently.Once the noodles are heated, add in the sauce & coleslaw mix. Stir to combine and allow to cook until the sauce is heated and coleslaw has started to soften. Add in the oranges, toss to combine and allow to cook for just a minute or two longer.
